    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>摘要：Markdown语法的使用 <span id="more"></span></p><br><h2 id="0-创建一个-md文件"><a href="#0-创建一个-md文件" class="headerlink" title="0.创建一个.md文件"></a>0.创建一个.md文件</h2><p>最好使用带预览功能的编辑器进行编辑，比如VScode，在VScode中安装拓展<code>Office Viewer(Markdown Editor)</code>，即可即时预览。使用该拓展打开.md文件后，可以在菜单栏点击<code>Edit In VSCode</code>进行语法编辑。<br>预览效果如下：  </p><p><img src="/20220810/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/markdownpreview.png" alt="Markdown Preview"></p><h2 id="1-标题"><a href="#1-标题" class="headerlink" title="1.标题"></a>1.标题</h2><figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 标题<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">## 标题<span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">### 标题<span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">#### 标题<span class="number">4</span></span><br><span class="line">##### 标题<span class="number">5</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：<br><img src="/20220810/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/titlepreview.png" alt="Title Preview"></p><br><h2 id="2-段落"><a href="#2-段落" class="headerlink" title="2.段落"></a>2.段落</h2><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是第一段</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这是第二段</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><blockquote><p>这是第一段</p><p>这是第二段</p></blockquote><br><h2 id="3-换行"><a href="#3-换行" class="headerlink" title="3.换行"></a>3.换行</h2><p>在一行的末尾加2个以上空格，再按回车<br>或者在末尾添加标签<code>&lt;br&gt;</code></p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是第一行，最后有2个空格  </span><br><span class="line">这是第二行<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">这是第三行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：  </p><blockquote><p>这是第一行，最后有2个空格<br>这是第二行<br><br>这是第三行</p></blockquote><br><h2 id="4-强调"><a href="#4-强调" class="headerlink" title="4.强调"></a>4.强调</h2><p>注意代码中的空格</p><h3 id="4-1文字加粗"><a href="#4-1文字加粗" class="headerlink" title="4.1文字加粗"></a>4.1文字加粗</h3><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">加<span class="strong">**粗**</span>啦</span><br><span class="line">加 <span class="emphasis">__粗__</span> 啦  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：  </p><blockquote><p>加<strong>粗</strong>啦<br>加 <strong>粗</strong> 啦  </p></blockquote><br><h3 id="4-2斜体"><a href="#4-2斜体" class="headerlink" title="4.2斜体"></a>4.2斜体</h3><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">变<span class="strong">*斜*</span>啦</span><br><span class="line">变 <span class="emphasis">_斜_</span> 啦</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：  </p><blockquote><p>变<em>斜</em>啦<br>变 <em>斜</em> 啦</p></blockquote><br><h3 id="4-3粗体-斜体"><a href="#4-3粗体-斜体" class="headerlink" title="4.3粗体+斜体"></a>4.3粗体+斜体</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">变<span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*粗斜*</span>**</span>啦</span><br><span class="line">变 <span class="strong">__<span class="emphasis">_粗斜_</span>__</span> 啦</span><br><span class="line">变 <span class="strong">__<span class="emphasis">*粗斜*</span>__</span> 啦</span><br><span class="line">变 <span class="emphasis">_<span class="strong">**粗斜**</span>_</span> 啦</span><br><span class="line">变 <span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">_粗斜_</span>**</span> 啦</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：  </p><blockquote><p>变<em><strong>粗斜</strong></em>啦<br>变 <em><strong>粗斜</strong></em> 啦<br>变 <strong><em>粗斜</em></strong> 啦<br>变 <em><strong>粗斜</strong></em> 啦<br>变 <strong><em>粗斜</em></strong> 啦  </p></blockquote><br><h2 id="5-引用"><a href="#5-引用" class="headerlink" title="5.引用"></a>5.引用</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash">这是一句引用</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash">这是一段引用</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash">这是一段引用</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-bash">&gt;这是一段引用</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash">&gt;引用还可以嵌套</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash">&gt;&gt;嵌套还可以嵌套</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-bash">&gt;引用里还可以放别的东西：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash">- 比如一个列表</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-bash">&gt;比如一张图片（我网上随便找的头像）![比如一张图片](/20220810/Markdown语法/unnamed.jpg)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">&gt;</span><span class="language-bash">还可以让我的字变**粗**，变***斜***</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><blockquote><p>这是一句引用  </p></blockquote><blockquote><p>这是一段引用<br>这是一段引用</p><p>这是一段引用</p><blockquote><p>引用还可以嵌套</p><blockquote><p>嵌套还可以嵌套</p></blockquote></blockquote><p>引用里还可以放别的东西：</p><ul><li>比如一个列表</li></ul><p>比如一张图片（我网上随便找的头像）<img src="/20220810/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/unnamed.jpg" alt="比如一张图片"><br>还可以让我的字变<strong>粗</strong>，变<em>斜</em></p></blockquote><br><h2 id="6-列表"><a href="#6-列表" class="headerlink" title="6.列表"></a>6.列表</h2><h3 id="6-1有序列表"><a href="#6-1有序列表" class="headerlink" title="6.1有序列表"></a>6.1有序列表</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> 这是一个列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> 这是一个列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">3.</span> 这也是一个列表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><ol><li>这是一个列表</li><li>这是一个列表</li><li>这也是一个列表</li></ol><br><h3 id="6-2无序列表"><a href="#6-2无序列表" class="headerlink" title="6.2无序列表"></a>6.2无序列表</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 这是一个列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+</span> 这是一个列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 这也是一个列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    *</span> 列表嵌套列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    1.</span> 嵌套有序列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    2.</span> 我是有序列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &gt; 在列表里嵌套其他东西</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">* 这是一个列表，可以套一张图片</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    ![比如一张图片](/20220810/Markdown语法/unnamed.jpg)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 套代码也可以</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>code1code 2<figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>这是一个列表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre><p>效果如下：</p><ul><li>这是一个列表</li></ul><ul><li>这是一个列表</li></ul><ul><li><p>这也是一个列表</p><ul><li>列表嵌套列表</li></ul><ol><li>嵌套有序列表</li><li>我是有序列表<blockquote><p>在列表里嵌套其他东西</p></blockquote></li></ol></li><li><p>这是一个列表，可以套一张图片</p><p>  <img src="/20220810/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/unnamed.jpg" alt="比如一张图片"></p></li><li><p>套代码也可以</p>  <figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">code1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">code</span> <span class="number">2</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>这是一个列表</p></li></ul><br><h2 id="7-代码"><a href="#7-代码" class="headerlink" title="7. 代码"></a>7. 代码</h2><h3 id="7-1普通代码"><a href="#7-1普通代码" class="headerlink" title="7.1普通代码"></a>7.1普通代码</h3><p>使用反引号 <code>`</code></p><figure class="highlight autohotkey"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">`比如这样`</span><br><span class="line">``或者这样``</span><br><span class="line">```这样也可以```</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：<br><code>比如这样</code><br><code>或者这样</code><br><code>这样也可以</code>  </p><br><h3 id="7-2代码块"><a href="#7-2代码块" class="headerlink" title="7.2代码块"></a>7.2代码块</h3><p>（由于缩进的方法在一些场合，比如我的blog，会无法显示，在这里不做介绍）<br>代码块要这样打：</p><figure class="highlight arcade"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">``</span><span class="string">`</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">我是代码</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">`</span><span class="string">``</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>也可以这样打：</p><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~~</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">我是代码</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">~~~</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我是代码</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我是代码</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><h3 id="7-3代码根据编程语言自动高亮"><a href="#7-3代码根据编程语言自动高亮" class="headerlink" title="7.3代码根据编程语言自动高亮"></a>7.3代码根据编程语言自动高亮</h3><p>比如C++</p><figure class="highlight arduino"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">```c++</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;<span class="number">100</span>;i++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;alen&#x27;s blog&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">```</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;<span class="number">100</span>;i++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;alen&#x27;s blog&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="8-分割线"><a href="#8-分割线" class="headerlink" title="8.分割线"></a>8.分割线</h2><p>分割线可以这样打：</p><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">***</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet"></span><span class="section">或者</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br><span class="line">或者</span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">___</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：<br><code>***</code>：</p><hr><p><code>---</code>：</p><hr><p><code>___</code>：</p><hr><br><h2 id="9-超链接"><a href="#9-超链接" class="headerlink" title="9.超链接"></a>9.超链接</h2><p>超链接到一个网址：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是一个链接 [<span class="string">Alen&#x27;s Blog</span>](<span class="link">https://chenmoshaoalen.github.io/</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：<br>这是一个链接 <a href="https://chenmoshaoalen.github.io/">Alen’s Blog</a></p><p>给链接增加悬停显示：</p><figure class="highlight ada"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是一个链接 [Alen<span class="symbol">&#x27;s</span> Blog](https://chenmoshaoalen.github.io/ <span class="string">&quot;最牛的Blog&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：<br>这是一个链接 <a href="https://chenmoshaoalen.github.io/" title="最牛的Blog">Alen’s Blog</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
